channel.description:
Hi, I was wondering if anybody could possibly help me solve a problem with my server. The last thing I did before I started getting the error was after I got done editing the Defence level requirements for some items. I go to compile the server and it compiles fine with 0 errors. Then once I run the server I get somekind error and I get kicked off when I try to login. Here's what happens:
1. I compile the server. No errors found. [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img359.imageshack.us/img359/4365/compilerdp8.png[/img][/URL]
2. I run the server. I get the exception error. [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img527.imageshack.us/img527/6331/runserverua6.png[/img][/URL]
Could somebody please help me figure out what's wrong? If you need anymore pictures or information please contact me on here or you can reach me on Xfire, MSN, or Yahoo.
Xfire - irsniper MSN - teddy_pimp6400@hotmail.com Yahoo - chris_breezy156@yahoo.com
Thanks for your time, Chris
